# Agent source tree is excluded from the image (Tauri/Rust, multi-GB),
# but the *built installers* under glanus-agent/builds/ MUST ship — the
# /api/downloads/[filename] route streams them from disk at runtime, so
# without them the download-agent flow returns 404 in production.
glanus-agent
!glanus-agent/builds
!glanus-agent/builds/**

